SUMMARY:Turn Daily Workflows into AI Agents — A No-Code Workshop with MuleRun
DESCRIPTION:Premium Small-Group Online Workshop\nBuild real AI Agents from real industry workflows. \n​This premium small-group\, hands-on online workshop is designed for experienced professionals who want to turn real-world workflows into working AI Agents using MuleRun’s agent-building platform. \n​Unlike general AI introductions\, this session is execution-focused. \n​You will work on your own workflow or recurring industry use case — and leave with a functional AI Agent prototype. \n​🎁 Awards & Incentives\n​🥇 1st Prize: $200\n🥈 2nd Prize: $150\n🥉 3rd Prize: $100 \n🎟️ All participants receive $20 MuleRun Plus subscription credit \n​Awards are evaluated based on:\n• Clarity of problem definition\n• Practical execution\n• Strength of workflow logic\n• Real-world usability \n​⚠️ No coding background required. \n​🔥 What Makes This Workshop Different\n​• Premium small-group format (limited seats for meaningful interaction)\n• Bring a real workflow → leave with a working AI Agent\n• No-code building experience\n• Live guidance and real-time feedback\n• Clear path to publish and iterate \n​This is not a webinar.\nThis is structured\, hands-on building. \n​🧠 By the End of the Session\, You Will\n​• Build a functional AI Agent based on your own workflow\n• Structure agent logic around decisions\, actions\, and outcomes\n• Test and refine your Agent\n• Publish your Agent to the MuleRun Agent Store \n​⚙️ Workshop Structure (3 Hours)\n​🧭 30-minute framework walkthrough\nCore concepts\, workflow-to-agent thinking\, and setup best practices \n​🛠️ 2 hours of hands-on building\nParticipants build their own agents with live guidance \n​🎤 30-minute demo & judging session\nParticipants present their agents and receive feedback \n​👤 Who Should Join\n​This workshop is best suited for: \n​• Industry professionals with 5+ years of experience\n• Founders and operators\n• Consultants and domain experts\n• Corporate leaders exploring AI integration\n• Builders looking to prototype practical tools \n​Participants are strongly encouraged to come with a specific workflow or use case in mind. \n​⚠️ This is not a general AI introduction session. \n​About MuleRun\n​MuleRun is one of the world’s largest AI agent platforms and agent stores\, serving millions of users globally. \n​On MuleRun\, users can: \n​Discover and use AI agents built by others across a wide range of use cases \n​Build their own AI agents using MuleRun’s agent tools \n​Publish agents to the MuleRun Agent Store\, making them available to other users \n​Generate revenue when others use or subscribe to their agents \n​MuleRun provides an open platform where ideas can be quickly turned into usable\, shareable\, and monetizable AI agents. （Learn more at: mulerun.com） \n_________\nAbout B.E.L.L.E\nWe are B.E.L.L.E (Boundless; Entrepreneurship; Liberty; Liaison; Empowerment)\, a community of entrepreneurs dedicated to breaking boundaries and building futures. \nOur Impact: We’ve connected over 25\,000 people\, supported more than 600 startups\, and collectively they raised $1 billion in funding!
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/turn-daily-workflows-into-ai-agents-a-no-code-workshop-with-mulerun/
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence,Developer,Educational events,Startups
