SUMMARY:Insforge x Qoder AI Agent Hackathon – $3\,000 Cash Prize
DESCRIPTION:Build the next generation of autonomous AI agents — together. \n​🌍 What’s This About?\n​AI isn’t just the future — it’s happening now. Join a community of mission-driven developers\, designers\, and builders for a one-day\, in-person hackathon focused on building autonomous AI agents and AI-powered applications that solve real-world problems. \n​This hackathon centers around the powerful combination of Qoder and Insforge\, providing a full end-to-end AI-native development stack: \n​Qoder — An Agentic IDE designed for real software development. It transforms how AI understands code; beyond snippets\, it grasps your entire architecture\, dependencies\, and patterns. \n​Insforge — An Agent-native Backend Platform that lets your coding agents build and run the backend for you. Add Auth\, DB\, Storage\, and Serverless functions to your app in seconds. \n​Together\, these platforms enable a new way of building software: AI agents that don’t just write code\, but also test it\, connect it to real backends\, and ship production-ready systems. \n​🎯 Agenda\n​09:00 AM – Doors Open & Check-In \n​09:30 AM – Opening & Platform Demos (Qoder & Insforge) \n​09:50 AM – Team Formation & Ideation (Teams may also be formed in advance through our Discord channel.) \n​10:00 AM – Hacking Begins 🚀 \n​12:00 PM – Lunch Served 🍕 \n​04:00 PM – Project Submission Deadline ⏳ \n​04:15 PM – Pitches & Demo Showcase \n​05:15 PM – Judging & Networking \n​05:45 PM – Awards Ceremony 🏆 \n​06:00 PM – Event Concludes \n​🏆 Prizes — $3\,000 Total Pool\n​🥇 1st Place – $1\,000 \n​🥈 2nd Place – $800 \n​🥉 3rd Place – $500 \n​🧪 Best Use of Qoder – $350 \n​🚀 Best Use of Insforge – $350 \n​🛠️ Rules\n​Pre-planning encouraged: Feel free to come with ideas\, diagrams\, and architecture ready to go. \n​Team Size: Teams of up to 3 people. \n​In-person only: This is a build-and-vibe day in Seattle; remote participation is not available. \n​Respect & Inclusion: Mandatory. We are here to create a safe space for bold ideas and collaborative building. \n​💡 Pro Tip: While you are welcome to use any tools you like\, projects that best demonstrate the synergy between Qoder and Insforge will stand out significantly to the judges. \n​🧩 About the Hosts & Partners\n​Qoder: The world’s first Agentic IDE built for real-world software engineering. It acts as an autonomous collaborator that understands entire codebases and executes multi-file edits to help developers ship faster. \n​Insforge: An Agent-native Backend Platform that enables AI coding agents to build and operate production-ready backends in seconds\, bridging the gap from prototype to scalable applications. \n​B.E.L.L.E Community: A global community of entrepreneurs dedicated to breaking boundaries. We’ve connected over 25\,000 members and supported 600+ startups that have collectively raised over $1 billion.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/insforge-x-qoder-ai-agent-hackathon-3000-cash-prize/
LOCATION:1700 Westlake Ave N #200\, Seattle\, WA 98109
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence,Developer,Hackathons,Startups
