SUMMARY:ctrl+alt+create live: Vibe Coding for Everybody
DESCRIPTION:​https://ctrlaltcreate.live/ \n​Anybody Can Build Software with AI. No Experience? We’ll Help You Get Started. \n​One Registered Participant Will Get a $100 Amazon Gift Card! \n​Presented by Every\, this is a community-oriented\, beginner-friendly workshop series that’s fun for techies & non-technical people alike. \n​Register to participate either in-person (in Seattle) or online. \n​If you need to use AI but don’t know where to start\, this is for you. If you’ve been building with AI\, then you’re also welcome! \n​We’ll help you build something in just 2 hours. Fast\, fun\, and zero skills required. And if you know what you’re doing\, great! \n​Seriously\, Anyone Can Build Something. \n​We’re bringing together non-technical users with big ideas and technical users who share a passion for AI and vibe coding. It’s a creative melting pot where curiosity meets capability. \n​Learn how to begin: We show you how to use AI tools that respond to plain English. It’s easy to get started with vibe coding. \n​2-Hour Sprint: Fast\, high-energy\, and satisfying. You could walk away with a real project or prototype. \n​Low Stakes\, High Reward: Experiment without fear. Plus\, a random attendee will get a $100 Amazon Gift Card! \n​In-Person & Virtual: We host regular workshops in tech hubs like Seattle\, while welcoming virtual participants from anywhere in the world. \n​All Ages Welcome: Kids and students are encouraged to participate alongside adults. \n​Who Is This For? \n​The Daydreamer: Would-be entrepreneurs who have never launched their own idea. Turn “what if” into a functional prototype in two hours. \n​The Idea Hunter: Curious entrepreneurs waiting for inspiration to strike. Test concepts quickly and find your next big venture. \n​The Tech-Adjacent: People who work in tech but aren’t software developers. Master the tools that allow you to build without engineering tickets. \n​The Upskiller: Looking for work or better positioning? Build a portfolio of AI-powered projects to prove your value in the modern workforce. \n​The Creative: Artists\, designers\, or writers. Learn how to bridge the gap between your imagination and a working digital product. \n​The Experimenter: This is your chance to try AI tools or build with low stakes. No pressure\, no wrong answers—just create.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/ctrlaltcreate-live-vibe-coding-for-everybody/
LOCATION:Foundations\, 1605 Boylston Ave\, Seattle\, 98122\, United States
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/CtrlAltCreate.jpg
END:VEVENT
