SUMMARY:Seattle (AI) Startup Summit 2026
DESCRIPTION:​This is Not a Generative AI Event. This is an AI-Driven Startup Summit. \n​Forget the hype cycle. Join the focused gathering of AI founders\, deep-tech investors\, and executive decision-makers who are actually building and funding the next generation of intelligent systems. The Seattle Startup Summit is your nexus for the applied AI ecosystem. \n​What You Will Gain: \n\n​📈 The Investor Thesis: Get exclusive access to Venture Capitalists and Angel Investors actively writing checks for AI-first business models. Learn what VCs are really looking for in LLMOps\, Agentic AI\, and specialized foundation models (pre-seed to Series A).\n​🛠️ Deep-Tech Deployment: Move from prototype to production. Sessions focus on the hardest technical challenges: Inference Optimization\, Data Strategy (Data as Moat)\, and Cost-Efficient Scaling of massive models.\n​⚖️ Governance & GTM: Navigate the new regulatory landscape. Dive into discussions on AI Governance\, Ethical Frameworks\, IP/Data Rights\, and how to build a go-to-market strategy that wins enterprise trust.\n​🤝 High-Value Connections: This is a curated assembly. Network directly with the engineers\, researchers\, and founders from Seattle’s most prominent AI companies who are defining the global standard.\n\n​Register now to build your AI advantage and secure your funding future. \n​Find our more at seattlestartupsummit.com. \n​2025 Stats: \n\n​Over 40% of attendees were in leadership positions\n​Over 55% of attendees were in an engineering role\n​Over 450 unique companies participated\n​Over 50 companies came to exhibit\n​Almost 900 people signed up\n\n​For 2026\, you can expect: \n\n​80-100 companies to exhibit\n​1200 – 1500 attendees\n​120 Top Tier AI Companies vying for the top category prize
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/seattle-ai-startup-summit-2026-2/
LOCATION:Sheraton Grand Seattle\, 1400 6th Avenue\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-17-100637.png
